cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use macMLX in your research or project,
  please cite it using the metadata from this file.
type: software
title: macMLX
abstract: >-
  Native macOS LLM inference application powered by Apple MLX.
  Provides a SwiftUI GUI for managing and running local language models
  on Apple Silicon via an OpenAI-compatible API.
authors:
